{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_51_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 千紗からのプレゼント",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 5.3156162873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、大体書けたわね。後はこれを……\nあら、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I’m almost done.\nOh‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3312866957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "それって、雑誌のお誕生日企画のアンケートだよね\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』、だっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the questionnaire for that birthday feature in the magazine‚ right?\n“Miracle☆Idol Birthday!”‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、誕生日に合わせて\nやってみたかったことを叶えてくれるみたいなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ they’re supposed to\ngrant you a wish you’ve always wanted to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど今、書き終わったところよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just finished filling it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4768482048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、見てもいい？\nふむふむ、お姉ちゃんのやってみたいことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ can I see it?\nHmm‚ hmm‚ what you want to do is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "『最近疲れ気味な千紗のために\nマッサージを勉強したい』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I want to learn how to give massages‚\nfor Chisa.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "『月ストのために、ランキング上位のアイドルを\n研究して今後に生かしたい』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I want to study top-ranking idols\nand use that knowledge for Moon Tempest in the future.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん、私のためとか、月ストのためとか\nこれじゃあいつもと変わんないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sis‚ you’re writing about things for me or for Moon Tempest‚\nbut that’s the same as always~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのお誕生日なんだから、我慢しないで、自分の\n好きなこととか、やりたいことを書いた方がいいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it’s your special birthday‚\nyou should write down what you like or want to do without holding back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0076888482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "我慢してるつもりはないんだけど……\nあっ、それなら、こういうのはどうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not holding back‚ though…\nAh‚ then how about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6613099427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "新しいお願い事？　えっと、『外食が多い子のために\n栄養たっぷりのご飯を作ってあげたい』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new wish? Let’s see‚ “For children who eat out a lot‚\nI want to cook nutritious meals.\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6268990227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ～、お姉ちゃんってば～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ sis!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.2808208863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1052837928
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1052837928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど～\nそれで千紗ちゃんがかわりにアンケートを書いてるのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see~.\nSo‚ Chisa’s filling out the questionnaire for you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3333325705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0929284652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、{user}さんにお願いして\n編集部の人達に連絡を取ってもらったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I asked {user}-san\nto contact the people at the editorial department.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.166668447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんって、真面目で優しいから\nいつも周りのことを優先しちゃうんだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister is so serious and kind that\nshe always puts others first…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666735334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 112.4367006223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、お姉ちゃん自身が楽しめる一日を\n私からプレゼントしたいなって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I wanted to give her a day where she could have fun‚\nas a present.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.2333351137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 119.4766982316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、素敵な一日になりそうね\nどんなことをしようと思ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ it sounds like it’ll be a wonderful day.\nWhat are you planning to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666659039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 125.4709615944
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "まずはショッピングかなぁ\n最近、新しい服がほしい、って言ってたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ I was thinking we could go shopping.\nShe’s been saying she wants some new clothes lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9690568824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7222364344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "後、ライブを観に行こうかなって\n実はお姉ちゃんには、推しのアイドルがいるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then maybe we could go see a live performance.\nActually‚ she has a favorite idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3000043234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "研究とかとは別で、ファンとして\n好きなグループがあってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aside from all the research stuff‚\nshe has a group she likes as a fan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6866160409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 145.1317528165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "それに、お気に入りのホラー映画もあるんだよ。のめり\n込み過ぎて、観てる途中で気絶しちゃってたくらいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She also has a favorite horror movie. She got so engrossed in it\nthat she almost fainted while watching it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4999931337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "あの映画の続編って、まだ上映してたかなぁ\n終わっちゃってたら、グッズを買いに行くとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if the sequel to that movie is still playing?\nIf it’s over‚ maybe we could buy some merchandise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7666598004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 162.1786050349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ホラー映画は、分からないけど……さすが妹だわ\n沙季ちゃんの好きなこと、沢山知ってるのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know about horror movies… But you’re a good sister.\nYou know a lot about what Saki likes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4333254498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 170.6150164045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あんまり予定を詰め込んじゃうと\n移動が多くならないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you pack the schedule too tightly‚\nwon’t there be a lot of traveling around?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.1021920691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 175.3918187853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そこは大丈夫\n移動が楽しみになる工夫を考えてあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ don't worry about that!\nI’ve got a trick to make moving around fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.5999921164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.9578533248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
